title: DDFP 374: AFC East preview & camp stories
itunes:title: DDFP 374: AFC East preview & camp stories
description:
Shek is joined by Bucky Brooks and Ike Taylor to preview the New England Patriots and the rest of the AFC East. Then, Nate Burleson joins the crew to share some training camp stories and discuss the keys to having a Super Bowl team. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
